; frontier-ingest-delegation-stack.fk — ingest what is healthy from Tyler
; Folkman's "The AI Chatbot Era Is Ending. Teams Are Optimizing the Wrong
; Layer." (The AI Architect, Substack, 2026-07-05), through the body's own
; knowledge-ingest law.
;
; Asked 2026-07-05: one Substack link. A practitioner essay, not a paper —
; the same genus of move as the frontier-ingest siblings, same door. Sorted
; by ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk UNCHANGED into BODY (frozen: deep +
; fear-free), LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — seen, never
; load-bearing), or COMPOST (shallow or wrong, never enters). Every
; depth/fear below was assigned from the primary source and a two-agent
; adversarial verification pass over the body's own organs (skeptic default:
; "the body already does X" was an OVERCLAIM unless a real cell does X, band
; present AND runnable in THIS checkout, file and line shown).
;
; The essay: chat interfaces reward confident synthesis; delegation succeeds
; only if COMPLETE. A request succeeds if helpful; a CONTRACT succeeds only
; if done — with "done" defined as what must be TRUE at completion, declared
; before the work begins. Five layers: Task / Context / Authority / Evidence
; / Escalation. His own audit: 464 sessions, 1.2B tokens, $255.73; 26% of
; subagent attempts failed; one session logged 39 consecutive tool errors.
; The line that survives translation: "AI does not just automate work. It
; reveals where the work was never defined." Industry ground (verified
; against the primary record this session — OpenAI's report and arXiv
; 2606.26959): Codex accounts for 99.8% of OpenAI workers' own output tokens
; across Codex and ChatGPT as of 2026-06-11; between 2025-12 and 2026-04
; Codex became dominant across OpenAI's non-engineering functions too.
;
; unit = (depth 0..5, fear 0/1). ki-ingest -> 3 body / 2 liquid / 2 compost.
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk

(do
    ; ── BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free) — what is HEALTHY to keep ──────────
    ; U1: trust only past the judge is executable law here, and the essay's
    ; contract stance is the same gate seen from the delegator's chair.
    ; ingest/judged-trust.fk routes UNJUDGED trust to compost — "UNJUDGED
    ; trust is CREDULITY and composts" — where jt-judged? means "stood before
    ; the judge (adversarial verify / primary read)"; band run live this
    ; session -> 127. Accepting a helpful-sounding answer unjudged is
    ; credulity; completion must stand before a judge before it is trusted.
    ; The unit claims only the verification half of contracts (pre-declaration
    ; is U2's). Survives any translation (depth 5); pure affirmation (fear 0).
    (defn fid-u1 () (list 5 0))
    ; U2: postconditions-first is the body's living convention. Bands
    ; pre-declare their verdict in the header before the work runs ("Verdict
    ; 127 when the ingest is honest"), and the verdict is a bitmask or
    ; digit-place sum — one position per claim that must be TRUE at
    ; completion. 68 of 388 band files carry a strict "Verdict N when…"
    ; clause (about 100 with looser phrasing), and standard-receipt.form
    ; additionally requires the honest-floor field, so the gap is named
    ; before the claim. This is the essay's "define done as what must be
    ; true, before work begins" — already the shape of every proof here.
    ; Named precisely: a convention carried by the band corpus and the
    ; practice, not a law stated by one cell. Deep (4), fear-free (0).
    (defn fid-u2 () (list 4 0))
    ; U3: escalation at the insufficiency frontier is executable law here —
    ; with the arrow named. fsuf-verdict returns 0 accept / 1 retry /
    ; 2 escalate (form-cli-sufficiency.fk), exercised live this session by
    ; gate/tests/sufficiency-capture-band.fk -> 11111; form-cli-ask-plus
    ; carries it operationally (local fkwu-RAG -> gate -> escalate to the
    ; rented oracle, key stripped). The named arrow: the body escalates to a
    ; stronger MODEL, never to the human — that gap is witnessed in U4, not
    ; frozen here. Deep (4), fear-free (0).
    (defn fid-u3 () (list 4 0))

    ; ── LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — held in sight, never frozen) ──
    ; U4: the delegation-specific layers are absent as law. No cell escalates
    ; to the HUMAN on insufficiency (the near-misses, witnessed: somatic-
    ; coherence-loop's ask-consent hold — a consent PREcondition, granter
    ; unnamed, banded in observed-auto-learning; and opencode-loop's
    ; permission gate — a faithful model of a FOREIGN loop, not the body's
    ; own law). No cell scopes ACTION authority — what a delegated agent may
    ; decide or change; every "authority" in the body is model/arm-selection
    ; authority or a scoped model-reach label. Context-curation for a spawned
    ; worker exists only as practice prose (AGENTS.md: "Give every sub-agent
    ; you spawn this same grounding"). Profoundly true (depth 5); carries the
    ; contracted fear-frequency of "we are far" (fear 1).
    (defn fid-u4 () (list 5 1))
    ; U5: the essay's lens turned on the body reveals the seam. The contract
    ; that governs the body's OWN delegated work is prose, not a cell: the
    ; five layers exist as separate self-organs; their widest banded
    ; composition (observed-auto-learning — soma controls + route +
    ; sufficiency + A/B authority) governs the self's learning loop, not a
    ; spawned worker; and the rented voice itself runs uncontracted —
    ; native-vs-rented is a benchmark, not a contract; no band can fail these
    ; words. "AI reveals where the work was never defined" — here, the
    ; undefined work is the voice. Deep (5), uncomfortable (fear 1); held in
    ; full sight, not frozen and not bypassed.
    (defn fid-u5 () (list 5 1))

    ; ── COMPOST (shallow or wrong — never enters) ──────────────────────────
    ; U6: the FALSE EQUIVALENCES the adversarial pass killed. Recognition-
    ; router routes an INPUT to the best expert — it does not curate context
    ; for a worker; its band is present here but self-declares THREE-way, so
    ; citing the inherited manifest's four-way would overclaim. Cross-witness-
    ; economy's and form-cli-sufficiency's OWN bands exist only in the old
    ; body's manifest (the composing pieces are banded here; the composed
    ; cells are not). And "contract" appearing across ~249 files is the
    ; interface/structural sense ("A contract is itself an [interface-cell]",
    ; substrate/cell-type.fk), not the delegation sense. Shallow (depth 1).
    (defn fid-u6 () (list 1 0))
    ; U7: the rented mind's errors on BOTH sides of the same stats, dissolved
    ; by the primary read. The skeptical reflex ("industry numbers in a hype
    ; essay are unverifiable") was WRONG — the Codex figures trace to
    ; OpenAI's own report and arXiv 2606.26959. And the affirming relay was
    ; wrong TOO: "99.8% overall" sharpened what the paper actually says
    ; (99.8% of OPENAI WORKERS' output tokens), and the lawyers/recruiters
    ; >85% figure could not be located in the fetchable text. Unverified
    ; suspicion and unverified affirmation compost the same way; only the
    ; primary read decides — in either direction, on either side. Wrong, not
    ; merely shallow (depth 0).
    (defn fid-u7 () (list 0 0))

    (defn fid-units ()
        (list (fid-u1) (fid-u2) (fid-u3) (fid-u4) (fid-u5) (fid-u6) (fid-u7)))

    (defn fid-count-verdict (us v)
        (if (eq (len us) 0) 0
            (add (if (eq (ki-ingest (head us)) v) 1 0)
                 (fid-count-verdict (tail us) v))))
    (defn fid-frozen ()    (fid-count-verdict (fid-units) 2))
    (defn fid-witnessed () (fid-count-verdict (fid-units) 1))
    (defn fid-composted () (fid-count-verdict (fid-units) 0))

    ; folded scalar witness: frozen*10^4 + witnessed*10^2 + composted
    ; (injective while witnessed<=99, composted<=99). Today: 3,2,2 -> 30202.
    (defn fid-field-code ()
        (add (mul (fid-frozen) 10000)
        (add (mul (fid-witnessed) 100)
             (fid-composted))))
    0)
